Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! I'm here to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:10.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:20.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:22.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:26.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:16.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get my calligraphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:19.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Got it a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:24.58,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Stars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:24.58,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,73)}Seishu Handa"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:28.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,With its size, it's quite a piece to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,0:01:29.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:34.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying it wouldn't look good if it was small?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:36.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:39.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he's learning,\NKawafuji is technically an art dealer...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:42.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just technical, and that's why he only praises size?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:44.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Or is size the only thing about it worth praising?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:47.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Bothersome as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:50.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now calm down. The Director should be here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:55.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can I get a glass of water...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:58.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You look pale...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:04.99,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"I'm in Tokyo"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:04.99,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,73)}"Translation: Yoseo"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:11.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to say to the Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:14.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "what"? Just apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:17.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're back because the\NDirector said he'd forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:20.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is just a matter of how you feel about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:23.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did buy these cell straps as a gift...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:26.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Straps? He isn't a high-school girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:29.64,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Baramon-{\i1}kun"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:30.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not cute at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:39.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your sighing is starting to depress me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:42.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The Director is going to be looking at my calligraphy shortly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:47.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do if he criticizes it before I submit it to Naruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to recover from it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:52.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it'll be criticized.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:55.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You sent this over because you were confident in it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:03:01.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We've known each other for a while.\NWhat's your take on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:04.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Would you have known it was something I wrote?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:09.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,\NI'm not sure how to reply, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:13.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...the calligraphy is bold and draws attention. I think it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:16.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have expected this based on your previous style.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:17.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:18.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:21.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't... write this kind of calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's too good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:26.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry, but I don't get a word you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:30.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How can I word this...?\NThis "off" feeling... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's like, it's {\i1}their{\i0} fault I wrote it, know what I mean? Like, it just {\i1}happened{\i0}, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.74,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"10 minutes later"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So you mean it was a fluke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Way to cut down on the details!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:42.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Anyone can write calligraphy like that if they go to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:45.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to be worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:49.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stop questioning yourself just because your style is different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:53.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just say you adventured a bit, and get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:57.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, I'll never be able to write my own calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,An aspiring farmer can't become a fisherman
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:05.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,just because he casually went fishing and caught a {\i1}hisanio{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:10.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find my own one-of-a-kind flower and nurture it until it blossoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want a special flower that's the only one of its kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:18.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you implying that you don't need to be number one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A farmer can't become a fisherman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:27.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Quite an interesting comparison, Handa-{\i1}kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:29.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:34.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Successful calligraphers and artists master their arts in like manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:36.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't greet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:39.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. I'm the one who wanted to meet Handa-{\i1}kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:41.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No formalities are needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Fine! And well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:51.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No need to be so tense...\NYou spoke more naturally before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:54.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No! I just got carried away back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:59.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down... Calm yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:02.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day I'm going to apologize and get forgiven...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:05.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A cane?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The Director must have an ailing back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:15.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Handa-{\i1}kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:23.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I was angry... how could\NI have punched a person like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a lowlife...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:42.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I should have apologized earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:47.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For my violent behavior, and for only facing you after hearing you would forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...truly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:55.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:59.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In all honesty, I wasn't going to forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:06.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I used my forgiveness as bait to bring you here, so that I could lecture you on morals, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:11.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...it seems that wasn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:16.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever act on impulse again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:25.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:29.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about what to do if I wasn't forgiven...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:31.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...so very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Handa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Go and give him that strap now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:41.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the right time to bring that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Handa-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to take a closer look at your calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind lending me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:10.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So this is your style of calligraphy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:11.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:19.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:25.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This calligraphy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:41.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I just told you not to act on impulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh... Don't laugh... Don't laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:47.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This work is just a sketch! Right!\NSomething I wrote for practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:52.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I packed my work for the exhibition, so I... uh, didn't bring it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:58.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It is unreasonable for me to have wanted to see your work so close to the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:02.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. I'm so sorry to have shown you my terrible calligraphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Handa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:10.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let me evaluate this based on the idea that it is just a sketch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:18.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your writing has become very interesting, unlike anything before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:23.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The character is reminiscent of an elementary school subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:26.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and yet I can see stars amid the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:29.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's the loneliness of being abandoned in darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:32.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but also the light that only darkness reveals...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:38.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the only judge on the panel, but I think this is grand prize-worthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:49.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If this is just a sketch, then I can expect something better at Naruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:54.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful day it has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:09:00.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Director? I'll call a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:09.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've really done it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.48,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Kawafuji Fine Arts"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No need for a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:15.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My ride is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:17.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:25.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Someone drove him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That car...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:40.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It seems sending Seishu-{\i1}kun{\i0} to the island was the right move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He still has a lot to improve on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I stalled the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not very good at starting the car on an incline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:54.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're just awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Both me and my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Y-You're scaring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:05.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Handa! Looks like your dad was here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:07.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Send me back to the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My, it's been a while, Kawafuji-{\i1}kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:32.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:34.80,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Naru" "flight" "island" "{\i1}konomon"{\i0}
