Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:36.86,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(525,135)}the island"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:49.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--I better leave...\N--Don't leave... you jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:53.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,From the looks of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:55.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...you haven't finished, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:56.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That hair of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:02.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is that to get back into the groove you were in on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:05.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I was hoping for a sliver of inspiration...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:08.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The deadline for the exhibit is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be doing stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:13.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No need to get so angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:17.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did write the "Stars" character like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:20.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? If you write in that style, you can shoot for the grand prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:23.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you wrote it like before, then you're set!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.61,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Stars
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.61,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,73)}Seishu Handa"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:29.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like something an elementary school student would write.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:35.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying to write the same as before, but I just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:39.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I tried staring at the stars, but the bright city lights don't allow me the needed anxiety!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:41.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can't write! Can't write! I just can't write...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Still, the difference is astounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:49.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just the type who gets swayed by the environment more than others...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:55.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That means your stability up to now was just because your life was so calm and placid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:58.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've submitted to a number of exhibits before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:04.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to say! If I could do this,\NI wouldn't have called the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:08.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"The likes of me"?\NI'm the only friend you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:09.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:11.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:14.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There is one thing you can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:29.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sei-{\i1}san{\i0}? I brought tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:34.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Is there any meaning to this?!\N--I can't bind you well. Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:36.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, who am I supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really like kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:40.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:46.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bondage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:48.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--B-Bondage...\N--Are you his mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:50.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?! Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:54.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sei-{\i1}san{\i0}... What are you doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! No, it's not what you think!\NThis is for my writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:00.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--This really isn't what it looks like, Mom!\N--By the way, Kawafuji-{\i1}san{\i0} is Naru-{\i1}chan,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:03.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Mom...?\N--and I'm the crybaby first grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:05.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He was such a good child...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He may have had a cold attitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:12.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but he was kind at heart, and loved by everyone as a {\i1}tsundere...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But now, he's more like a tsun-dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no "{\i1}moe{\i0}" involved whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:19.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because he went to the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:27.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:31.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, but this is seriously bringing back memories of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:36.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think it's too simple to expect that you'll be able write calligraphy well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:38.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...by mimicking what happened on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:46.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget about calligraphy you can only write on the island, and hurry back to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop searching!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! A dirty mag!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't toss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:14:00.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like submitting if\NSensei isn't going to submit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:06.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like the prize money is great or it'll make you famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:09.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should just write a bunch and open my own exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:14.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding? Do you know how much I'm staking on this exhibit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:17.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it's not a major exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:22.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But for me, this is an important step towards being reborn anew...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:25.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that step no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:32.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop recording me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My famous quotes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you bring him here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:39.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--I figured Naru alone wouldn't be enough to lift your spirits.\N--S... Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:47.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...your seriousness was answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:51.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:53.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A call?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:58.59,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"On Hold"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:01.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So did we get through?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We got through?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Sensei!\N--Sensei, how ya doin'?!\N--Hey, lemme speak too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! He's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:16.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there, Sensei! How ya doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:20.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei? Kawafuji-{\i1}san{\i0} told me that you were lonely, and he wanted us to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aki! Ya finished yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:25.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So I gathered everyone at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:27.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:33.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kawa-{\i1}san{\i0} is so kind! But Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0} is also really worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:35.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:37.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:40.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--You sure did cause problems,\N--My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--leavin' without a word like that.\N--Hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:44.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Sorry about--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:49.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are ya okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop sayin' useless stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:53.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna knock ya out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Great having a friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:57.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You better appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:15:59.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, me next!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:01.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ouch! You're stepping on my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:05.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah... Thanks.\N--Sensei! Are you doing okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:08.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He thanked me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:11.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're hurting my ears! Take turns talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:14.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Sensei? Yer coming back, right?\N--Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When ya gonna come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:20.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We thought of the perfect penalty for you leaving without tellin' us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:22.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:28.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you were stressed over not being able to come up with a good piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're that worried for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:34.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are attentive, even more than most adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:39.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll be fine if I can remember things from the island to arouse my inspiration...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:46.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's seriously going to a kid with his problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:51.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not a slump per se, but when I try to write, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hina doesn't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Tell me when someone else gets on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is being played with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:01.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Sensei?\N--Is that you, Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:02.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:05.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's boring 'round here without you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:09.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I still got a lot I wanna do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:11.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:13.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...hurry and come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:20.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're waitin' for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:30.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can you write now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:34.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:44.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not sure if I brought it with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It was the last work I did back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:00.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? A name list?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Ink.\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Make me plenty of ink!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki, go and buy me some paper to practice on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:08.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, he's finally on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:15.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he isn't going to do anything strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was against him leaving in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:20.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever want him to go back to the island again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:23.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then go and convince him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:25.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What a horrible person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know he's going to want to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sending me to get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're so horrible! Horrible! Horrible!...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:36.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're partly to blame for\NSei's overly serious nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:40.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're not the ones to determine our son's potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:48.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If going off on his own will make him mature, all we can do is watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:53.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the way of manhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:58.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! It's Handa Seimei!\NHe's so refined and cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:38.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kawafuji. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:44.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's my greatest masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:58.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Pretty amazing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:01.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've written calligraphy like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And the title?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stone Wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:44.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The summer assignments are going to be posted in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:46.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go and take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:48.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:51.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:52.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:55.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We may get the gold award, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:58.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If we're awarded, Sensei will be so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:01.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's surprise Sensei with a double gold award!
